They are both warriors in their respective careers and also their striking resemblance has left some Mzansi fans thinking out loud... Daniel Cardoso may have had a nightmare game against Maritzburg United in the Telkom Knockout this past weekend but he's done enough to impress the Amakhosi supporters since he joined the club. He has become a penalty taker of note with his calmness, composure and coolness when he takes the spot-kick.According to Wikipedia, Boyka is a professional Russian prison fighter who appears as an antagonist in the Undisputed II film, and later became the main protagonist of the third film to the latest Undisputed film. He was portrayed by Scott Adkins. 